U.S. Oct. Equipment and Finance Industry Confidence

-- B y   A l e x   T a n z i
-- 
2011-10-21T12:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/u-s-oct-equipment-and-finance-industry-confidence-table-.html
Confidence in equipment financing strengthened 
in October, according to the Equipment Leasing & Finance Foundation.
The index is formulated from a survey of 50 organizations to gauge
business confidence in the $650 billion equipment finance industry.  The survey consists of seven questions and an area for comments:
•Current business conditions
•Expected product demand over the next four months
•Access to capital over the next four months
•Future employment conditions
•Evaluation of the current U.S. economy
•U.S. economic conditions over the next six months
•Business development spending expectations
•Open ended question for comment  SOURCE: Equipment Leasing and Finance Foundation  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alex Tanzi in Washington at   atanzi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Babic at   mbabic@bloomberg.net  